{"tid":2183651,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭: 孕婦過馬路被黑警撞 丈夫不應斥責引起衝突","createTime":"2020-09-01T05:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T07:24:49.000Z","uid":123774,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"065e9092e82b5ee9e9eec268ed6125fd0dd39e32","tid":2183651,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:13:38.000Z","msg":"「無衝突 就唔需要警察執法」<br />\n<br />\n衝突 - 係因為黑警撞人老婆 丈夫據理力爭<br />\n執法 - 原來包括推低手無寸鐵嘅孕婦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YCxKVZN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYCxKVZN.jpg&h=64eaf9f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n似唔似皇軍? <br />\n難怪堅持唔三權獨立<br />\n要徹底改變香港憲制<br />\n<br />\n新三為一體<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z00sTMG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz00sTMG.jpg&h=a50c3b49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方昨晚在旺角執法期間，懷疑推跌一名孕婦，她其後需要送院，目前仍然留院，情況穩定。行政長官林鄭月娥表示，該名孕婦在警方執法期間出現一些不舒服，警方已經表示關注，她本人當然亦表示關注，不希望再發生有關事情。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，有關問題需要正本清源，如果社會沒有發生衝突、暴亂和打交，就不需要警方執法，社會一段很長時間不斷聚焦警方執法，但忘記警方執法的原因，強調警方執法是維護社會治安和人身安全。林鄭月娥說，從電視畫面看到，當時相對混亂，警方在執法過程發生一些大家不願意看到的事情，事後需要評估和檢討，往後在這方面是否能夠做好。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547175-20200901.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547175-20200901.htm&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7sLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=8c684f48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547175-20200901.htm&h=1dad497d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547175-20200901.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d3a077918185c92ee3eb16cf45f7a68b9e05e6de","tid":2183651,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:15:43.000Z","msg":"皇軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/a